OL,3,COlivia Deansgate: Station name change
OL,4,Cdubbed 'confusing'
OL,6,FManchester's Deansgate railway station
OL,7,Fhas undergone a quirky transformation
OL,8,Fthis week, temporarily rebranded as
OL,9,F"Olivia Deansgate" as the city
OL,10,Fprepares to host the BRIT Awards for
OL,11,Fthe very first time.
OL,13,FThe UK's biggest music awards ceremony
OL,14,Fis set to take place at Manchester's
OL,15,FCo-op Live on Saturday 28 February,
OL,16,Fwith global stars like Harry Styles,
OL,17,FROSALIA, Mark Ronson, and Olivia Dean
OL,18,Fall set to perform.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@RO]
