PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772025561
OL,3,COlivia Deansgate: Station name change
OL,4,Cdubbed 'confusing'
OL,6,FNorthern Rail marked the occasion with
OL,7,Fa playful nod to one of this year's
OL,8,Fmost-nominated artists, Olivia Dean,
OL,9,Fby changing the station signage - a
OL,10,Fmove that has already got commuters in
OL,11,FManchester talking.
OL,13,FSome commuters were left scratching
OL,14,Ftheir heads at the new signs, with one
OL,15,Fsocial media user calling it "a
OL,16,Fproject designed to confuse tourists
OL,17,Fand those who rely on these signs."
OL,26,@wD@^OUyD@cO]
