PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772025561
OL,3,COlivia Deansgate: Station name change
OL,4,Cdubbed 'confusing'
OL,6,FNorthern Rail responded to the
OL,7,Fdiscussion, assuring passengers that
OL,8,Fthe change is only temporary and "the
OL,9,Fsigns will change back after" the
OL,10,FBRITs.
OL,12,FOlivia Dean, who has hits including
OL,13,F"Man I Need" and "Nice To Each Other,"
OL,14,Fwill not only perform at the BRITs but
OL,15,Fwill also play a special show at
OL,16,FManchester's Albert Hall during BRITs
OL,17,FWeek.
OL,26,@pD@bOUqD@]O]uD@AOUuD@LO]uD@ROUuD@fO]
