PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772025561
OL,3,COlivia Deansgate: Station name change
OL,4,Cdubbed 'confusing'
OL,6,FShe'll be joined at the awards
OL,7,Fceremony by a star-studded lineup that
OL,8,Fincludes Sombr, HUNTR/X, Wolf Alice,
OL,9,FAlex Warren and more.
OL,11,FWith thousands expected to descend on
OL,12,FManchester for the BRITs and millions
OL,13,Fmore tuning in live, the city is set
OL,14,Ffor a week packed with music, events,
OL,15,Fand celebrations - proof that, for one
OL,16,Fweek at least, Manchester really is
OL,17,Fthe UK's music capital.
